    "The network was trained for 200 ms with a minimum desired decision error of 0.05.",
    "The results indicate that to achieve a working memory of 1200 ms, τ b1 and τ b2 need to be 30 and 300 ms, respectively.",
    "However, increasing τ b2 to 500 ms led to an even faster convergence of the LSNN network for the same working memory.",
    "Compared to the working memory value with the DEXAT model, these values of τ b1 and τ b2 are much smaller.",
